{{#> layout title="Action Required: Company Association Needed"}}
    <h2>Important: Company Association Required</h2>
    
    <p>Hello {{userName}},</p>
    
    <div class="message-box">
        <p class="text-large">⚠️ Action Required</p>
        <p>Your account requires association with a company to maintain full access to our procurement platform.</p>
        <p>Deadline: <span class="highlight">{{lockDate}}</span></p>
    </div>

    <p>You have two options to resolve this:</p>
    
    <div class="message-box">
        <p class="text-large">Option 1: Join an Existing Company</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Click "Join Company" below</li>
            <li>Search for your company</li>
            <li>Submit a join request</li>
            <li>Wait for approval from company management</li>
        </ul>
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 15px 0;">
            <a href="{{joinCompanyUrl}}" class="button">Join Company</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="message-box">
        <p class="text-large">Option 2: Register a New Company</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Click "Register Company" below</li>
            <li>Provide company details</li>
            <li>Submit required documentation</li>
            <li>Wait for verification by our team</li>
        </ul>
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 15px 0;">
            <a href="{{registerCompanyUrl}}" class="button">Register Company</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="message-box">
        <p class="text-large">Important Notes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Your account will be locked on {{lockDate}} if no action is taken</li>
            <li>Company verification may take up to {{verificationDuration}} business days</li>
            <li>Ensure all submitted documentation is current and valid</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <p class="text-small">Need help? Contact our support team for assistance with the company association process.</p>
{{/layout}}
